results.title: FREE SHIP Live Love Laugh scrabble tile decor
Live Simply, Dream Big, Be Grateful, Give Love, Laugh Lots-  Quote/Saying/Poem - Wall Art Print
results.description:
Live Simply, Dream Big, Be Grateful, Give Love, Laugh Lots.

An inspirational, uplifting and motivational quote; great for a gift or your own home decor. This print features a stunning seascape background and brings colour into any room in the house.

The frame is not supplied.

The print is handmade and printed to order.

It is available in two sizes:

A4: 21cm x 29.7cm
A3: 29.7cm x 42cm

Our prints are printed on high-quality FSC certified 230gsm matte white photo paper.

Environmental
All our prints use FSC (Forest Stewardship Council) certified paper, harvested in a responsible manner. The FSC is recognised by the WWF as the 'hallmark of responsible forest management'. 

We make our prints to order to prevent any unnecessary wastage.

We send these prints in natural non-bleached 100% recycled brown paper envelopes that are card-backed to prevent any damage.

The envelopes can be easily recycled - please check with your local authority for details of recycling in your area.

We use XL ink cartridges where available. When our cartridges are used, they are donated to raise funds for Whale and Dolphin  Conservation.

About Honeste
Honeste is small local sustainable British homeware and gifting brand run by two friends - Katherine and Louise. Along with being as sustainable as we can, we love to incorporate designs and influences from our families cultural backgrounds: Britain, Thailand, India and China.

We think about how we can be eco-conscious in all aspects of our business and each product's description will give you information about how that product is greener or eco-friendly. This may be from how it was grown and sourced, the materials used and the production. Our office is powered by 100% renewable electricity and all our packaging is eco-conscious as well.

We send all our orders using brown recycled cardboard boxes or envelopes. We then use recycled brown paper to protect our products in the boxes. Envelopes used are also made from 100% recycled paper. We use brown paper tape to seal our boxes so everything is recyclable and biodegradable. We send receipts and delivery notes electronically; please message us if you want a printed receipt included. Any branding on packaging is hand stamped using plant-based, vegan, non-toxic ink.

We donate 10% of all our profits to charity. We have currently shortlisted several charities and will be announcing our chosen charity partner soon.

We recycle all our old ink cartridges to prevent them from going to landfill. We recycle the cartridges by donating them to  Whale and Dolphin Conservation (WDC) via The Recycling Factory. WDC, Whale and Dolphin Conservation, is a global charity dedicated to the conservation and protection of whales and dolphins. Should the cartridges not be on the eligible list via the Recycling Factory at the time of donating, we will donate to another recycling programme and donate all proceeds to charity.

results.title: LAUGH Crocheted Dishcloth Pattern - PDF File Only
results.description:
LAUGH!!!  Crocheted Dishcloth Pattern!!!

After releasing my knitted dishcloth patterns I had so many requests for crocheted ones so here you go!!!   :) These are fully written patterns that have been tested by several crocheters!!!  :) 

These dishcloths seem to be all the rage and I have customers messaging me daily placing orders!!!  I had an ad on a local buy and sell group and I had to remove the ad because I was overwhelmed with the amount of orders received in such a short period of time .

This listing is for a pattern and you will not receive anything in the mail.  It's an automatic download and once purchased it will be found under your purchases!!

results.title: PS I LOVE YOU antiqued distressed prim sign for that special someone, Valentine's Day, Rustic Style Just enough to Say those special words
results.description:
"P.S. I love you." This is a great gift that will remind your special someone you love them everyday! Rustic Style, simple but a touch of class.

* This sign measures approximately 5.5 x 12 inches and is on 3/4 inch thick wood. 
*This creation is shown in Brown/Light Pink. 
• Several other color options available in drop down selection. The first color will be the color of the text & second color will be the background.

• Shipment is generally 3 to 5 business days.

• Hanger attached on backside for easy hanging

• Hand painted laser engraved creation is made to order.

• If we are shipping directly as gift, we can enclose a small handwritten note card, be sure to let us know what you want the card to say in the note section.

• PROCESS Our handcrafted creations are made using a 7 step process to create a beautiful expression to be cherished for years to come. Two contrasting colors of paint are applied, the design is laser engraved, a fine hairline is applied to the design which gives an awesome touch. The final touches are completed once it goes through our antiquing process with edges distressed.

• COLOR We have a variety of color choices, but if you don't see what you are looking for, please ask  & we will see if we can make it happen for you. Keep in mind when selecting the color options, the first color is the text color, while the second color is the background. See policies for additional questions/clarification on colors.

• Please note these signs are not massed produced but each is unique and no two are exactly the same.

• When working with wood and the antiquing process, each sign has its own warmth and charm. While we try to get the best wood at the lumber yard, sometimes there will be knots or other slight imperfections in the wood, this is considered adding character to the rustic style of this line of our signs. Thanks for stopping by our shop and please do not hesitate to ask any questions.

Be sure to check out our other signs. https://www.etsy.com/shop/ExpressionsNmore?ref=hdr_shop_menu

Color Samples can be seen in a variety of sizes at  https://www.expressionsnmore.com/color-examples-rustic-laser-engraved/
